@startuml
!pragma layout smetana
title 11A. Supervisor Review / Task Lifecycle

skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> REQUEST_RECEIVED
REQUEST_RECEIVED --> HITL_EVALUATING
HITL_EVALUATING --> PLAN_FROZEN_FOR_REVIEW : review required\n(or fail-closed review path)
HITL_EVALUATING --> RUNNING : review not required
PLAN_FROZEN_FOR_REVIEW --> WAITING_REVIEW : snapshot(versioned execution input) stored

WAITING_REVIEW --> SNAPSHOT_VERIFIED : tasks/review/decide APPROVE
WAITING_REVIEW --> CANCELED : tasks/review/decide CANCEL
SNAPSHOT_VERIFIED --> RUNNING : resume_token + state_version + request_hash + frozen_plan_hash valid
RUNNING --> COMPLETED
RUNNING --> FAILED

CANCELED --> [*]
COMPLETED --> [*]
FAILED --> [*]

note right of WAITING_REVIEW
This is review/task lifecycle state.
It is outside the graph runtime state machine.
Reviewed execution snapshot must already exist.
end note

note right of SNAPSHOT_VERIFIED
Approval does not rebuild plan from raw request.
Execution resumes from immutable reviewed snapshot.
Resume entry point is ROUTING_SELECTED, not PLANNED.
end note
@enduml

@startuml
!pragma layout smetana
title 11B. Supervisor Runtime Execution State Machine

skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> REQUEST_VALIDATED
REQUEST_VALIDATED --> HISTORY_LOADED
HISTORY_LOADED --> PLANNED
PLANNED --> ROUTING_SELECTED
HISTORY_LOADED --> ROUTING_SELECTED : approved snapshot resume\n(plans already frozen)
ROUTING_SELECTED --> A2A_CALLING : plans exist
ROUTING_SELECTED --> COMPOSING : no plan / max iteration reached

A2A_CALLING --> HANDOFF_EVALUATING
HANDOFF_EVALUATING --> HANDOFF_APPLIED : accepted handoff exists
HANDOFF_EVALUATING --> HANDOFF_SKIPPED : none / rejected / flag disabled
HANDOFF_APPLIED --> A2A_RESULT_MERGED
HANDOFF_SKIPPED --> A2A_RESULT_MERGED
A2A_RESULT_MERGED --> ROUTING_SELECTED : next plan exists
A2A_RESULT_MERGED --> COMPOSING : all plans consumed
COMPOSING --> COMPLETED
COMPLETED --> [*]

note right of REQUEST_VALIDATED
SupervisorRuntimeState values:
- REQUEST_VALIDATED
- HISTORY_LOADED
- PLANNED
- ROUTING_SELECTED
- A2A_CALLING
- HANDOFF_EVALUATING
- HANDOFF_APPLIED
- HANDOFF_SKIPPED
- A2A_RESULT_MERGED
- COMPOSING
- COMPLETED
end note

note right of HANDOFF_EVALUATING
Policy checks
- feature flag
- route allowlist
- method allowlist
- stream support
- max hops / recent path
end note

note bottom
HITL waiting is not a graph runtime node.
The runtime state machine starts only after execution is admitted.
Approved snapshot resume skips PLANNED and starts from frozen routing queue.
Planned P2 extensions:
- REVISED
- WAITING_FOR_USER_INPUT
end note
@enduml
